    <title>2022国庆川西游</title>
    <url>/2022/11/12/travel202210/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="行程"><a href="#行程" class="headerlink" title="行程"></a>行程</h2><h3 id="新津-康定情歌广场"><a href="#新津-康定情歌广场" class="headerlink" title="新津-康定情歌广场"></a>新津-康定情歌广场</h3><p>10月1日在新津吃了顿老字号的<a href="https://surl.amap.com/kZm9iQul2w3">爆花汤锅</a>，晚上开始出发。</p>
<p>晚上乌漆嘛黑，唯一的风景就是隧道群</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/vx20221112200532.jpg" alt="隧道群"></p>
<p>中间到一个服务区休息一下</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/VX20221112201854.jpg" alt="天全服务区"></p>
<p>出高速,做完核酸到康定情歌广场看这条河，大半夜找不到吃的,还好有家<a href="https://surl.amap.com/lPV0zZQ1280L">普通面馆</a>,还不错。</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/IMG_0754.JPG" alt="康定广场"></p>
<h3 id="康定-鱼子西"><a href="#康定-鱼子西" class="headerlink" title="康定-鱼子西"></a>康定-鱼子西</h3><p>导航到鱼子西三村看星空和日出，是一条水泥小路，一直开到星空露营地，还好是深夜，路上鬼都没有，最后一段路烂得扣胩。</p>
<p>繁星</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/IMG_0769.JPG" alt="星空"></p>
<p>鱼子西上，从北到南可以看雅拉雪山，四姑娘山和贡嘎雪山</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/IMG_0804.JPG" alt="雅拉雪山"></p>
<p>日出</p>
<div id="dplayer0" class="dplayer hexo-tag-dplayer-mark" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"></div><script>(function(){var player = new DPlayer({"container":document.getElementById("dplayer0"),"video":{"url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/IMG_0809202211122054521.mp4"}});window.dplayers||(window.dplayers=[]);window.dplayers.push(player);})()</script>

<p>打完卡下山去，打算去墨石公园</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/IMG_0834.JPG" alt="鱼子西"></p>
<h3 id="鱼子西-八美镇-新都桥"><a href="#鱼子西-八美镇-新都桥" class="headerlink" title="鱼子西-八美镇-新都桥"></a>鱼子西-八美镇-新都桥</h3><p>10月2日，路上风景绝美</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/IMG_0849.jpeg" alt="雅拉雪山"></p>
<p>墨石公园要钱没去，直接去新都桥，车少路好，敞开飚，开车也是一种享受。</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/IMG_0896.jpeg" alt="zoomzoom"></p>
<p>中途还骑个马儿</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/IMG_0873.jpeg" alt="驾"></p>
<h3 id="新都桥-红海子-康定"><a href="#新都桥-红海子-康定" class="headerlink" title="新都桥-红海子-康定"></a>新都桥-红海子-康定</h3><p>10月3日，再开一遍新都桥，中途登顶折多山，海拔4千多米，不算太高，但还是能体验到缺氧的感觉。</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/VX20221112222110.jpg" alt="折多山"></p>
<p>然后去红海子，不要门票，迎着雪山前进不要太爽</p>
<div id="dplayer1" class="dplayer hexo-tag-dplayer-mark" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"></div><script>(function(){var player = new DPlayer({"container":document.getElementById("dplayer1"),"video":{"url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/VID_20221003_144042.mp4"}});window.dplayers||(window.dplayers=[]);window.dplayers.push(player);})()</script>

<div id="dplayer2" class="dplayer hexo-tag-dplayer-mark" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"></div><script>(function(){var player = new DPlayer({"container":document.getElementById("dplayer2"),"video":{"url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/IMG_1015_Trim.MOV"}});window.dplayers||(window.dplayers=[]);window.dplayers.push(player);})()</script>

<p>红海子就一个小湖</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/vx_20221112222354.jpg" alt="红海子"></p>
<p>回康定的路上又是不一样的风景</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/IMG_20221003_162557.jpg" alt="层林尽染"></p>
<h3 id="康定-碧峰峡-成都"><a href="#康定-碧峰峡-成都" class="headerlink" title="康定-碧峰峡-成都"></a>康定-碧峰峡-成都</h3><p>10月4日，做完核酸准备打道回府，感觉时间还够顺便看了下碧峰峡，回去是白天，可以欣赏路上风景。</p>
<div id="dplayer3" class="dplayer hexo-tag-dplayer-mark" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"></div><script>(function(){var player = new DPlayer({"container":document.getElementById("dplayer3"),"video":{"url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/IMG_1065_Trim.MOV"}});window.dplayers||(window.dplayers=[]);window.dplayers.push(player);})()</script>

<p>碧峰峡风景区没啥看的</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/VX20221112220940.jpg" alt="碧峰峡"></p>
<p>动物园有逛头，可惜没去，就看了看大熊猫，这熊猫表演完就下班</p>
<div id="dplayer4" class="dplayer hexo-tag-dplayer-mark" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"></div><script>(function(){var player = new DPlayer({"container":document.getElementById("dplayer4"),"video":{"url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/kolomomo/pic_repo/PicGo/travel/vx_20221112222530.mp4"}});window.dplayers||(window.dplayers=[]);window.dplayers.push(player);})()</script>

<p>吃完雅鱼，高高兴兴回家^-^.</p>
]]></content>
